title: Roy Gaines - 1998 - Bluesman For Life FLAC
description:
Roy Gaines - 1998 - Bluesman For Life

Genius' is a much over used and abused term, but it is the only fitting description one can think of when attempting to describe the talents and accomplishments of Waskon, Texas-born Roy Gaines, The Blues Guitar Superman.
Having had the pleasure of speaking with Roy for several hours for a recent two-part interview in Real Blues Magazine, I can say that I'm astounded, given his illustrious career and long list of achieve- ments, that he is not as famous as a dozen lesser stars of blues guitar especially since Roy could easily play rings around any and all competition. (Andy Grigg)
